# Project Overview

## Project Description
* CodeMentor AI is an AI-powered knowledge assistant designed to help developers quickly find solutions, generate code snippets, and understand complex programming concepts. It integrates with various developer tools and provides real-time responses using LLMs.

## Objectives
* Develop an AI-powered knowledge assistant for developers
* Provide real-time responses to user queries
* Integrate with various developer tools
* Supports natural language queries.
* Generates code snippets, documentation, and explanations.

## Technologies

* Backend: FastAPI, Python, SQL
* Frontend: Next.js, Three.js
* LLM Tools: LangChain, LangSmith, LangServe, LangGraph, CrewAI
* Cloud & DevOps: AWS, Docker, Jenkins, Git
* Testing & Documentation: Postman, Swagger

## Features
* AI chatbot for developers
* Interactive knowledge graph
* CI/CD pipeline for deployment

